{
  "texts": [
    "The impact of AI on communication and the last mile challenge in EWSs remains uncertain.",
    "While it becomes challenging to envision how AI could assist vulnerable communities struggling with basic needs, there are specific communication challenges where AI may excel.",
    "Adjusting warnings to the local context, providing interactivity, and doing so in native languages are areas where AI, especially ChatBots, could be beneficial.",
    "These large language models (LLMs) are now good at in-context learning 88 meaning they can explain warnings in reasonable narratives and offer context-specific answers, as seen in flood disaster reporting 89.",
    "Applying such models globally, especially in the global south with diverse languages, presents challenges 90."
  ]
}